findings.title: Owner can change fees
findings.description: The owner has privileges to modify fees which could lead to potential security issues.

findings.title: Owner can change the maximum transaction amount and maximum wallet amount
findings.description: The owner has privileges to modify the maximum transaction amount and maximum wallet amount.

findings.title: Owner can change buyBackUpperLimit
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the buyBackUpperLimit, which could lead to potential security risks.

findings.title: Owner can exclude from the fee
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to exclude certain addresses or transactions from paying fees.

findings.title: Owner can change fee wallet
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to change the fee wallet.

findings.title: Owner can withdraw ERC tokens except native
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to withdraw ERC tokens excluding native tokens.

findings.title: Owner can lock and unlock
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to lock and unlock, which could allow them to retake privileges even after ownership was renounced.
